        public double getCmptbl()
        Getter for Compatibility of the couple. The compatibility of a couple is defined as the sum of: magnitude by which the budget of the boy exceeds the maintenance cost of the girl, the absolute value of the difference in attractiveness, and the absolute value of the difference of intelligence.
